<HEADLINE>
<P>
SAN DIEGO COUNTY DIGEST: LAKE WOHLFORD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
A badly decomposed body was found Monday about 1 mile northeast of Lake 
Wohlford, the Sheriff's Department reported. 
</P>
<P>
Investigators believe the victim is male, according to Sgt. Danny Goodrich. The 
partially buried body was discovered at 5:10 p.m., he said. 
</P>
<P>
Goodrich could not estimate when the victim died or the cause of death. An 
autopsy is pending. 
</P>
</TEXT>
