UNITED STATES; RIOTS -- SAINT CROIX; EMERGENCIES; UNITED STATES -- MILITARY AID 
-- VIRGIN ISLANDS OF THE UNITED STATES; EVACUATIONS; DISASTERS; VIRGIN ISLANDS 
