AGENCIES; POLICE -- LOS ANGELES COUNTY; DRUG SEIZURES -- LOS ANGELES COUNTY; 
DRUG ENFORCEMENT OFFICERS; POLICE CORRUPTION; EMBEZZLEMENT 
