<P>
Oakland voters strongly support local efforts to lure the Raiders back to the 
East Bay, a new poll shows. 
</P>
<P>
The poll, released by the Oakland-Alameda County Coliseum Board, said 60% of 
400 registered voters interviewed want the Raiders to return, while 21% don't 
approve of the idea and 19% have no opinion. 
