<TEXT>
<P>
Peter Lambert has been appointed senior vice president and manager of the newly 
formed entertainment industries division of World Trade Bank in Beverly Hills. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Column 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA092189-0186 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 110464 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
