ELDERS POSTS PROFIT DIP 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
From Reuters 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
MELBOURNE, Australia 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The giant Australian conglomerate Elders IXL reported a 5% fall in annual 
profits today despite an increased thirst for its Foster's lager. 
</P>
